The paper deals with influence maximization in social networks, specifically Twitter. This topic falls under the intersection of several CS sub-categories, including social networks (cs.SI), social and information networks (cs.SOC), information retrieval (cs.IR), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and databases (cs.DB). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
